Clone an stobject

Source: R/table-object.R
st_clone.Rd

Clone an stobject

st_clone(x)

Arguments

x

an stobject object.

Value

A copy (y) of x such that y can be modified without modifying x.

Examples

x <- st_new(stdata())
y <- st_clone(x)

y$data$STUDY <- NULL
x$data
